1. Berry Bros. & Rudd - Wine and spirits merchants to Her Majesty The Queen and His Royal Highness The Prince of Wales
2. Bentley Motors - Manufacturers of luxury cars for Her Majesty The Queen
3. Fortnum & Mason - Provisions and grocery store to Her Majesty The Queen and His Royal Highness The Prince of Wales
4. Gieves & Hawkes - Bespoke tailoring to His Royal Highness The Duke of Edinburgh and His Royal Highness The Prince of Wales
5. John Lobb - Bespoke and ready-to-wear shoes to His Royal Highness The Prince of Wales and His Royal Highness The Duke of Edinburgh
6. Hilditch & Key - Shirt makers to His Royal Highness The Prince of Wales
7. Barbour - Outerwear and clothing to Her Majesty The Queen and His Royal Highness The Duke of Edinburgh
8. Wartski - Jewellery, silver and objects of vertu to Her Majesty The Queen and His Royal Highness The Prince of Wales

These companies are just a few examples of the prestigious Royal Warrant holders in the UK. Each of them has been recognized for their commitment to quality, craftsmanship, and service, and their products are considered to be some of the best in their respective industries.
